headline: Northern Trust Releases Third Business Owner Benchmark
summary: CHICAGO, December 09, 2024--Business owners are forging ahead with big plans in 2025, according to The Northern Trust Institute’s third Business Owner Benchmark. The report, based on a survey of Northern Trust’s business owner clients, reveals that despite mixed feelings about the economy, many respondents are poised to undertake large scale changes within their business next year.

headline: Avanza Fonder Appoints Northern Trust to Provide Integrated Trading Solutions
summary: STOCKHOLM, December 09, 2024--Northern Trust (Nasdaq: NTRS) today announced its Integrated Trading Solutions (ITS) outsourced trading desk is supporting Avanza Fonder, a Stockholm-based fund company providing services for private clients.
